1.)	let's design an exam system to solve the modern days pandemic problem. The organization uses a multiple objective answering system to evaluate the students. but first you need to signup as a student then appear for the exam . After completion of the exam it shows the result and the correct answer of the respective questions. But there is two conditions first "one can only take the exam only once ' and the second one is whether the admin allows the students to take the exam or not .
